      "message": "@jaszczyk @jdudycz @kjaniak\nMaybe we should also drop `Count` suffix from variables names?\n\nReorganized names to feel more natural:\nreceivedMsgCount        -> receivedMessages\nconnectionsTotalCount -> totalConnections\ndisconnectionsCount    -> disconnections\nsentCount                     -> sentMessages\nsentToTopicCount         -> messagesSentToTopic\ndroppedCount              -> droppedMessages\ndroppedCauseCount     -> messagesDropCause\nclientsRejectedCount  -> clientsRejected\nclientsRejectedCauseCount  -> clientRejectionCause",
      "author": {
        "account_id": 3701,
        "name": "Filip Krzywka",
        "display_name": null,
        "email": "filip.krzywka@nokia.com",
        "username": "fkrzywka"
